chakkri ( ; from sanskrit cakrī चक्री , meaning " one who has a discus " , referring to the hindu god vishnu who possesses the discus sudarshana ) was the noble title of the civil chancellor ( สมุหนายก ) of ayutthaya , thon buri , and rattanakosin , the city - states in present - day thailand .

world travel : hua hin is a favorite seaside resort of this country 's ruling chakkri family ; their summer palace is there

